feat: wire Slack DMs for mentions and assignments (fl-4b0.14)

Add comment creation handlers (API + dashboard) that extract @mentions
and send Slack DMs to mentioned users via SlackBot.SendDM when a Slack
account mapping exists. Wire assignment handlers in both API and
dashboard to send Slack DMs to assigned users.

New package internal/slackdm provides the Sender type that handles:
- Resolving @mention names to accounts via AccountsByNames
- Looking up Slack user IDs via SlackUserIDForAccount
- Loading the project's Slack bot integration
- Sending DMs and creating in-app notifications
- Skipping self-notifications

